libqtshadowsocks (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Shadowsocks AEAD ciphers (SIP004/SIP007), requires botan-2
  * Shadowsocks SIP002 URI scheme support
  * OTA support is dropped
  * Minimum C++ standard is now C++14
  * Underlying refactoring and breaking changes
  * Logging formats improvements

 -- Symeon Huang <hzwhuang@gmail.com>  Wed, 15 Nov 2017 20:14:00 +0000

libqtshadowsocks (1.11.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * adds support for botan-2 (>=2.2.0)
  * uses botan as a private library (only in implementation)
  * migrates to use CMake as the build system

 -- Symeon Huang <hzwhuang@gmail.com>  Thu, 03 Aug 2017 21:53:00 +0100

